{
  "stem": "11722.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father was called in in 1942.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In other words, they were weakening our midst.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not in 1938 right away, but it happened-- it started in 19-- end of 1939 and 1940.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] kids could not go beyond the sixth grade in school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Jewish men had to have permission to travel certain distances.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was mild rules.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was-- it was-- they-- they just advanced the rules, you know, to 1943, '44, where they formed ghettos.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to stay in ghettos.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] I don't want to get ahead of myself because the-- the-- the-- the real cruelty started in 1943, the end of 1943 and 1944.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they had restrictions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was mild restrictions at a time, in comparison to what we had later on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember that I went to my father's factory, and I helped work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We all learned trades.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father became-- My-- my brother, my older brother, became a dental technician.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I helped out my dad's factory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, Jewish kids, at the age of twelve-- at the age of 12, had to give their time in service to the city.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were called the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], 'the youth,' where we had to-- the Jewish kids had to report in the morning.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had to go to these municipal places and sweep the grounds, and to sporting arenas and clean up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In other words, they just used us practically for slave labor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] as a kid-- that was on Fridays.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We would-- we would-- they would keep us sometimes till the Sabbath would set in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we still didn't get home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Sabbath was something that we all looked forward to.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
